The paper deals with the impact of transmit antenna selection on the secrecy performance of massive MIMO wiretap channels, which involves information theory (cs.IT), networking and internet architecture (cs.NI), cryptography and security (cs.CR), multimedia (cs.MM), and signal processing (cs.SI). Therefore, these are the most likely arXiv CS sub-categories for this paper.
